For Senior Resources - 7 Years plus

1) we have Invoice custom object. There is a custom button. Below requirements we need to cover. Write a code

	a) Agent can click on that it will convert it to Order and OrderLineItem. Anytime user can click on that button

	b) We have to prevent duplicate conversion of Invoice(Duplicate Order/OrderItem creation)

	c) If Any info update on invoice and Agent will click on button again it will update the info on Order/OrderLineItem

	d) Write a Process that will run daily and Utilize the same code on button click

2) We have two system one Salesforce and second MySQL. Currently Agent have to update the account and Invoice manually in both system. One account can have multiple Invoice in MySQL

	Design a proper solution to make the life easy of an Agent.

3) LWC Life Cycle

4) I want to log some integration information before data sent to external system(All possibilities).

5) We have a checkbox on account if it is checked record will hide to specific user and show some other user.

6) We have an existing org that have approx. 40k class and i want to monitor the org.
 
